{"type": "article", "id": 24862, "title": "我有一个故事，想用戒指告诉你", "description": "在如何把抽象的东西做得更具体这件事上，这个戒指成功了", "date": "2016-04-02T07:06:48Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 4595, "name": "戒指"}, {"id": 25739, "name": "微缩景观"}], "category": 17, "author": 474100, "comment_count": 15, "praise_count": 292, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702133413AGlxug8yVcLtobea.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>德国艺术家 Isabell Kiefhaber 是位热爱珠宝的设计师，最近她设计了一款带有微观景象的方形戒指，每个戒指都冰封着自己的故事。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133407eio09CVvwB2OHLhz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133408s0XEd2SuqPrJD7gi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>这些戒指用透明树脂做为原料，重量很轻，使用硅橡胶制作模具后倒入树脂，经过固化等步骤制成。每一只都是手工打造，在 <a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/shop/GeschmeideUnterTeck?zanpid=2150893399635991552&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_source=zanox&amp;utm_campaign=row_buyer&amp;utm_content=2156339\">etsy</a> 上出售，均价 99.42 美元。价格昂贵的最大原因在于它的独特性，戒指虽小，但里面定格的美好瞬间却在手指之间变得具象化起来。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133408NWKcvAoi1UODt3pg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133409F8tNqGfZ6kjJ17XM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133409lyhJN4E2Xdsk3FWV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">Isabell Kiefhaber 将生活中遇见的各种场景、人物和自然环境都定格到首饰中。<a href=\"http://www.boredpanda.com/miniature-worlds-inside-jewelry-isabell-kiefhaber/\">她说</a>，“我喜欢把人们常常忽略的生活细节作为首饰的灵感来源，所以把这些场景添加到首饰中，用平凡来吸引眼球，用自己的双手创造独一无二的珠宝。”<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133410FaISqGAExJTh6Nel.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133410t1iD9spGSnjzuaoE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133411iw7cCGS1QOk3xKBI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">一对老夫妇依偎在长椅上，一个中年男性在独自滑雪，母子寻路的身影，几只绵羊在草原漫步……世界由无数故事组成，Isabell 为人们展示了各种各样的故事，这些秘密的缘由只有定制戒指的人才有机会知道。<br></p>\n<p>这种微型景观创意并不少见，香港的两位创意工作者 Riyo 和 Howard 也推出过 100 个名为“<a href=\"http://www.shannnam.com/someone/fragmented-chronicles\">Fragmented Chronicles</a>”的戒指系列，将生活日常凝缩在透明戒指中。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133411hitSD3IosmEe5bQp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133412g2ZjHcqozOIBsbv5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6601467\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133412G9fJuUHmS85dhze2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6601467\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">生活还是需要一些梦幻感，Fragmented Chronicles 同样顺应了人们对童话世界的向往，无论是雪地修女还是带手提箱匆匆行走的路人，戒指中那些可爱风景和有趣的人物，都在等你用想象力或回忆去挖掘。</p>\n<p class=\"\">题图来自 <a href=\"http://blazepress.com/2016/03/tiny-dioramas-placed-inside-jewellery-by-isabell-kiefhaber/\">blazepress</a></p>\n\n"}